linder, we prove that the corresponding holonomy\nperturbation induces one of Goldman's generalized Hamiltonian twist flows on\nthe $SU(2)$ character variety $\\mathcal{M}(F)$ associated to the curve $C$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 1 Nov 2015 21:14:23 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 8 Nov 2015 17:41:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-11-10"}
